  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The propose of this study is to compare two methods of physical treatment for benign
      paroxysmal positional vertigo, by evaluating treatment effects on postural stability.

      The trail design is a double blinded randomized controlled trail, with each patient going
      through three evaluations: before treatment, 1 week after treatment and 60 days after
      treatment.
    </textblock>
